    <measure>Percentage of patients able to fully understand and fill out the german translation of the questionnaire.</measure>
    <time_frame>Patients suffering from dysphagia for at least half a year will be asked to answer the questionnaire at the time of enrolment.</time_frame>
    <description>Establishment of a questionnaire in german to determine in a structured and quantifiable manner the quality of life of patients with dysphagia.</description>
